{"title":"粮食［外一首］","authors":["刘昌庆"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食［外一首］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘昌庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾满地气和古风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总以金色的格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把秋天的情绪渲染得香喷喷的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有什么比粮食更加真实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地、风雨、节气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及铭刻在农人血液中的心事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食的意义不单纯是为了充饥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更重要的是教我们发芽茁壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥一把粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同攥满掌风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥一串泥土味儿的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻吹掉浮尘杂质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字珠玑大真大美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与粮食交谈的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语言是多余的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷是枣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷是娘一竿子一竿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从枣树上敲下来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他与无数红兜肚小娃娃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起在八月落地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是遍体鳞伤的命儿啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一辈子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风一棍子雨一棍子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲落了他一地碎梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年尘埃落定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷便是枣的爷爷了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实枣爷不是枣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷是棵枣树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣爷有坚韧的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有比骨骼更硬的心劲"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}